============================================================================
Additional Note Regarding Indigenous Cultural Identity
============================================================================

This work is Indigenous cultural expression authored by a First Nation logic
artist. The Indigenous identity of the work is part of its character and must
be preserved in attribution. Canadian law provides additional protections
for Indigenous cultural expression beyond standard copyright. Derivative
works must preserve the Indigenous attribution of the original source.

